  "id": "api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe",
  "title": "\n      DeprecatedDecimalPipe\n    ",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          \n            {\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 1,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\",\n              \"name\": \"API\"\n            }\n          }\n            ,{\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 2,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\",\n              \"name\": \"@angular/common\"\n            }\n          }\n            ,{\n            \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n            \"position\": 3,\n            \"item\": {\n              \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe\",\n              \"name\": \"DeprecatedDecimalPipe\"\n            }\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n      </script>\n    \n      \n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a>\n    \n      /\n      <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    \n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    <h1 id=\"deprecateddecimalpipe\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#deprecateddecimalpipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>\n      DeprecatedDecimalPipe\n    </h1>\n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n      <a href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#\"><label class=\"raised page-label\"><i class=\"material-icons\">mode_edit</i>suggest edits</label></a>\n      <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.5/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L61-L97\"><label class=\"raised page-label\"><i class=\"material-icons\">code</i>view source</label></a>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  \n<div class=\"what-it-does info-banner\">\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a number according to locale rules.</p>\n\n</div>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"how-to-use\">\n  <h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#how-to-use\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>How To Use</h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>number_expression | number[:digitInfo]</code></p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a number as text. Group sizing and separator and other locale-specific\nconfigurations are based on the active locale.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">where <code>expression</code> is a number:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> is a <code>string</code> which has a following format: <br>\n<code>{minIntegerDigits}.{minFractionDigits}-{maxFractionDigits}</code></li>\n<li><code>minIntegerDigits</code> is the minimum number of integer digits to use. Defaults to <code>1</code>.</li>\n<li><code>minFractionDigits</code> is the minimum number of digits after fraction. Defaults to <code>0</code>.</li>\n<li><code>maxFractionDigits</code> is the maximum number of digits after fraction. Defaults to <code>3</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">For more information on the acceptable range for each of these numbers and other\ndetails see your native internationalization library.</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">WARNING: this pipe uses the Internationalization API which is not yet available in all browsers\nand may require a polyfill. See <a href=\"guide/browser-support\">Browser Support</a> for details.</p>\n<h3 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"example\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Example</h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'deprecated-number-pipe',\n  template: `&#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;p>e (no formatting): {{e}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>e (3.1-5): {{e | number:'3.1-5'}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>pi (no formatting): {{pi}}&#x3C;/p>\n    &#x3C;p>pi (3.5-5): {{pi | number:'3.5-5'}}&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;/div>`\n})\nexport class DeprecatedNumberPipeComponent {\n  pi: number = 3.141592;\n  e: number = 2.718281828459045;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/browser-support\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#deprecateddecimalpipe\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#example\n - api/common/DeprecatedDecimalPipe#how-to-use\n - api/core/Component\n - guide/browser-support\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.5/packages/common/src/pipes/deprecated/number_pipe.ts#L61-L97\n-->"
